10:34.049 --> 10:37.953
I don't think it's going to be limited. I think we 
can work out bilaterals and regional agreements

10:37.993 --> 10:42.077
and international agreements. And I'm not really 
pessimistic about being able to do the kind of

10:43.629 --> 10:52.579
research we want to in the future. It's going to 
take a little bit more planning. And it may take

10:54.221 --> 11:04.474
some funding to solicit participation by some of 
those countries that we don't now do. But I think

11:05.475 --> 11:09.820
I'm pretty optimistic that we'll be able to go 
ahead and work.

